description: At least 40 people were killed and more than 100 injured when five gunmen dressed in camouflage opened fire with automatic weapons at people at a concert in the Crocus City Hall near Moscow, in one of the worst such attacks on Russia in years.
title: Gunmen kill 40 in attack at concert hall near Moscow

description: TEHRAN - Iran’s foreign minister says the Israeli war on the Gaza Strip for nearly six months has clearly laid bare the anti-human nature of the Zionists and that the West is using human rights just as a “political plaything”.
title: Gaza war shows the West using human rights as ‘political plaything’: Iranian FM

description: TEHRAN – Iran and Roma striker Sardar Azmoun has potentially suffered a season-ending injury in Iran’s latest match with Turkmenistan in the 2026 World Cup qualifier.
title: Sardar Azmoun sidelined for a month

description: Russia and China veto a UN Security Council draft resolution on Gaza proposed by the United States.
title: Russia, China veto US resolution on Gaza

description: TEHRAN - Nuclear energy has a significant impact on various sectors of the Iranian society and elevated Iran’s political status in the world, a top Iranian nuclear official says.
title: Nuclear technology has promoted Iran’s political status in the world: Kamalvandi

description: Rashida Tlaib, the only Palestinian American member of the US Congress, has accused the Israeli government of committing some of the worst crimes against humanity “of this century” in its war in Gaza.
title: Congresswoman: Israel using ‘starvation as weapon of war’

description: Israeli protesters marched on Thursday night near the home of Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu in Caesarea, south of Haifa, demanding the return of captives in Gaza and for national elections to be held early.
title: Israeli protesters march near Netanyahu’s home demanding early election

description: MADRID- As support for Israel plummets worldwide due to its brutal genocide in Gaza, there is a small group of Iranians who continue to back Israel: the followers of Reza Pahlavi, the son of Iran's deposed Shah.
title: Pahlavi and Israel: the old roots of a failed policy

description: The way Israelis view the war in Gaza really depends on who you speak to. Israel is an incredibly divided society. It has been for a very long time, but these fissures have come to the fore much more in recent weeks, particularly as the death toll in Gaza rises.
title: Israel a ‘very divided society’ as war drags on

description: MADRID- In his first speech of the year, Ayatollah Seyed Ali Khamenei analyzed the current situation of the country and outlined the objectives to be achieved during this new year of 1402.
title: The first message of the year by Ayatollah Khamenei: Reflections and Perspectives for the future
